<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I think it&apos;d be great for book club - there&apos;s definitely a lot to discuss! There&apos;s an essay from each year that Obama was in office, so it provides a <a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I think it'd be great for book club - there's definitely a lot to discuss! There's an essay from each year that Obama was in office, so it provides a historical framework. Coates prefaces each essay with his thoughts about the piece now, so you can analyze his analysis :)<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
