<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/53056522-mediocre"><img alt="Mediocre: The Dangerous Legacy of White Male America" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1569299522l/53056522._SX98_.jpg" />
